{"tid":1549793,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[KO藍絲]警察捉到派錢主腦未?","createTime":"2019-09-07T12:40:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T12:59:10.000Z","uid":134773,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"003289d285dd9536366a9eabf40e13a6badb919f","tid":1549793,"uid":134773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T12:40:54.000Z","msg":"都搞左3個月左右，拉左千幾人，又情報收集，又睇被捕人士電話，又派埋喬裝警員收風，應該可以追蹤到對話記錄 或 收入來源黎捉人 或 交收地點捉人?<br />\n<br />\n點解到依家都捉唔到主腦，無錢派仲有人出黎搞事? 都唔知啲警察做咩搞咁耐都捉唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />無撚理由<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />麻煩大家幫我問問身邊啲藍絲 thx."},{"pid":"910adcd9d4f3f9dee5c4bd5f49cb2ccf62ec458f","tid":1549793,"uid":123991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T12:41:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">出黎呀，自由閪！</div></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>不闖入、不塗鴉、不鐳射</strong></span></span><br />\n如有發現，批淮大家往死裡打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">明日之公眾集會(遮打花園)及公眾遊行(前往美領)已獲發不反對通知書。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n集會部分<br />\n地點：中環遮打花園<br />\n時間：13:30 - 18:30<br />\n四節主題：時代子民、獄中讚歌、審判將至、天佑美國<br />\n<br />\n※※ 遮打現場將收集香港人權與民主宣言聯署至14:30﹐隨後出發向美領遞交 ※※<br />\n<br />\n遊行部分<br />\n集合地點：中環遮打花園金鐘道出口<br />\n集合時間：14:30<br />\n遊行路線：遮打花園經花園道往下亞厘畢道巴士站公眾活動區，向美國領事館遞交請願信<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZY3Vs7C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZY3Vs7C.jpg&h=2d1d3d5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4a96cf69a147929fc3007d6b607359b08e1154f7","tid":1549793,"uid":258370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T12:42:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"54b4fa4ccfc551cdd577c6cefd6f80dc9214af00","tid":1549793,"uid":134773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"